# NSPrinter.TypeName

**Structure**

The type you use to describe a printer’s make and model.

## Declaration

```swift
struct TypeName
```

## Initializers

- **init(_:)**: Creates a printer type name.
- **init(rawValue:)**: Creates a new instance with the specified raw value.

## Getting General Printer Information

- **printerNames**: Returns the names of all available printers.
- **printerTypes**: Returns descriptions of the makes and models of all available printers.

## Conforms To

- Equatable
- Hashable
- RawRepresentable
- Sendable
- SendableMetatype
